data.description: No showings until 2/1/24. Approx. 4.25 acres of rolling, Middlebury Schools property & almost 4000SF! Set 600 feet off CR 4, this home offers: four bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, huge master bed/bath (twin sink, sunken tub/sep. shower, walk in closet w/built in dresser). Split bedroom floor plan, desk, 2nd full bath & mudroom/ML laundry. Bsmt: 4th bedroom (egress), possible 5th bedroom (no egress)/den/office/theater room, 1/2 bath (could be full bath) AND gigantic family room. Front porch, deck/patio, tons of parking, & att. garage. The heart of this HOME is truly in the custom kitchen, dining, and spacious living room. (Agents please read remarks; property is an estate and will be sold in As-Is condition.)
